Package: TooHotTooCold
Type: Package
Title: TooHotTooCold: A package to get your temperature just right
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Patrick English
Maintainer: Patrick English <p.english@sheffield.ac.uk>
Description: This package will help you achieve the optimum temperature through opening windows and changing your thermostat. Simply input how you are feelings and your thermostat and window information, and the package will come up with some helpful suggestions to get you feeling just right!
